Subject: drm/i915/crt: Populate connector->ddc
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 96f0ef50bfc646056a1a2ecf5a5b99888b97fe3c
